<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Ready Page</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="css/questions.css">
</head>



<header>
    <img class="logo" src="imgs/logo.png" alt="Company Logo">
</header>

<body>
    <div class="question" id="question1">
        <h2> Question 1:</h2>
        <p>What is a location (city) of this disco?</p>
        <img id="lomino_dance" src="imgs/lomino_dance.gif" alt="Company Logo">
        <input type="text" id="answer1" placeholder="Enter your answer here">
        <button class="btn-primary" onclick="checkAnswer1()"> Push Pop It</button>
    </div>

    <div class="question" id="question2">
        <h2> Question 2:</h2>
        <p>Who is a finance "mole" here, keeping an eagle eye on the bill to make sure it doesn't blow
            up?</p>
        <img id="finance_mole" src="imgs/second_question_image.png">
        <select id="question2_choices" name="choices">
            <option value="" disabled selected>Make a selection</option>
            <option value="answer1">The bill blew up and an infiltrator is taking a picture to open a case</option>
            <option value="answer2">An overly cheerful lady with her back partly turned towards us</option>
            <option value="answer3">The gentleman on the right in knitted by a grape on vacation sweater</option>
            <option value="answer4">All clearâ€”no watchdogs around</option>
        </select>
        <button class="btn-primary" onclick="checkAnswer2()"> Baby Bottle Pop It</button>
    </div>

    <div class="question" id="question3">
        <h2> Question 3:</h2>
        <p>Which customer, acting as its own district, is managed by this 'chef'?</p>
        <div class="scary_kevin">
            <img id="scary_kevin" src="imgs/kevin_cooking_with_a_scary_face.jpg">
        </div>
        <input type="text" id="answer3" placeholder="Chop up your answer here">
        <button class="btn-primary" onclick="checkAnswer3()"> Juicy Drop It</button>
    </div>

    <div class="question" id="question4">
        <h2> Question 4:</h2>
        <p>The real question should be "why", but let's answer "who" (first name) is on the left?</p>
        <img id="alan_taco" src="imgs/alan_taco.jpg">
        <input type="text" id="answer4" placeholder="Enter your answer here">
        <button class="btn-primary" onclick="checkAnswer4()"> Ring Pop It</button>
    </div>

    <script src="javascript/test.js" type="text/javascript" defer></script>


</body>

</html>